text: Phrynetopsis fuscicornis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Chevrolat in 1856. It has a wide distribution in Africa. It contains the varietas Phrynetopsis fuscicornis var. mystica.BioLib.cz - Phrynetopsis fuscicornis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1856
